And in Evans and Bulloch
counties in Georgia,

00:48:54.990 --> 00:48:57.630
rural counties, it was 11%.

00:48:57.630 --> 00:49:00.137
So that gives you some notion of how much

00:49:00.137 --> 00:49:01.920
intermixture has gone on.

00:49:01.920 --> 00:49:04.310
Various people who are
classified as Afro-American

00:49:04.310 --> 00:49:05.810
have various amounts of European

00:49:05.810 --> 00:49:08.780
and American Indian
ancestry, but on the average

00:49:08.780 --> 00:49:12.450
in the larger cities of the United States

00:49:12.450 --> 00:49:16.900
people have something like
20% to 25% European ancestry.

00:49:16.900 --> 00:49:20.840
And that's only been
going on in large amount

00:49:21.820 --> 00:49:26.273
presumably since the
beginning of the 19th century,

00:49:27.550 --> 00:49:29.113
or perhaps a little earlier.

00:49:30.050 --> 00:49:33.570
So the rate of infiltration of genes

00:49:33.570 --> 00:49:35.350
from one group into another

00:49:35.350 --> 00:49:38.420
where the groups themselves still maintain

00:49:38.420 --> 00:49:41.460
some kind of arbitrary
racial classification,

00:49:41.460 --> 00:49:42.293
and that's important.

00:49:42.293 --> 00:49:44.130
Look, this is an underestimate

00:49:44.130 --> 00:49:46.410
because it's only the
people who report themselves

00:49:46.410 --> 00:49:47.830
as being African American.

00:49:47.830 --> 00:49:49.190
How about all the people in this room

00:49:49.190 --> 00:49:52.406
who don't report themselves
as being African American,

00:49:52.406 --> 00:49:55.890
but like Pushkin have
an African grandfather

00:49:55.890 --> 00:49:56.820
or great-grandfather.

00:49:56.820 --> 00:49:58.700
Pushkin was a great guy.

00:49:58.700 --> 00:50:00.570
Alexander Pushkin's great-grandfather

00:50:00.570 --> 00:50:03.330
was a famous general, Russian general,

00:50:03.330 --> 00:50:05.180
who was, in fact, an African,

00:50:05.180 --> 00:50:08.600
who was a kind of Russian Othello.

00:50:08.600 --> 00:50:12.413
He became a very important
person in the Russian military.

00:50:13.820 --> 00:50:16.270
Pushkin would not have
reported himself as black,

00:50:17.140 --> 00:50:19.963
but 1/8 of his genes came from Africa.

00:50:21.000 --> 00:50:23.073
And that's important to understand that.

00:50:24.190 --> 00:50:26.190
Okay, you don't have to see the numbers.

00:50:27.610 --> 00:50:31.250
So you have fusion of populations

00:50:31.250 --> 00:50:35.450
but you also have, on
the the other face of it,

00:50:35.450 --> 00:50:40.330
a tremendous amount of local marriages

00:50:40.330 --> 00:50:43.000
and staying where you are,

00:50:43.000 --> 00:50:46.770
and you also have the effect of migrations

00:50:48.150 --> 00:50:50.970
and of conquests like the Icelanders

00:50:50.970 --> 00:50:54.050
which leave their genetic trace in places

00:50:54.050 --> 00:50:56.578
where they came in.

00:50:56.578 --> 00:50:59.443
And we could look at the next picture,

