This is a map of the frequencies
of the blood group, A,

00:51:29.180 --> 00:51:30.390
ordinary blood group A,

00:51:30.390 --> 00:51:33.520
in different parts of
England and Scotland.

00:51:33.520 --> 00:51:35.130
I don't know if you can see
it at the back of the room

00:51:35.130 --> 00:51:37.010
but the average frequency
in northern Scotland

00:51:37.010 --> 00:51:39.270
