It gets down to be 35%, 39%,
down to greater and greater.

00:51:43.570 --> 00:51:48.570
And just off the east
coast of England it is 46%.

00:51:51.940 --> 00:51:55.646
Now England, as you
know, is one of the most,

00:51:55.646 --> 00:51:59.350
as they used to say, bastardized
countries in the world.

00:51:59.350 --> 00:52:02.590
It is a consequence of invasions

00:52:02.590 --> 00:52:07.590
from Denmark and Saxony, from France,

00:52:09.370 --> 00:52:12.260
from the north of Vikings and so on,

00:52:12.260 --> 00:52:16.800
and what has happened is
that where the invaders land

00:52:16.800 --> 00:52:20.060
they leave their genes, quite locally,

00:52:20.060 --> 00:52:24.110
and even though those
invaders no longer arrived

00:52:24.110 --> 00:52:26.070
after the 11th century,

00:52:26.070 --> 00:52:30.590
the last time there was
serious invasions of England

00:52:30.590 --> 00:52:35.590
was the 11th century, their
genes have stayed around.

00:52:35.880 --> 00:52:40.540
And if you look, this part
of England which is called,

00:52:40.540 --> 00:52:41.690
I don't know how you
pronounce it in English,

00:52:41.690 --> 00:52:43.855
Dane-law or Dan-a-law,

00:52:43.855 --> 00:52:47.060
Danelaw, which has a lot of
