00:55:13.440 --> 00:55:14.490
Why is that?

00:55:14.490 --> 00:55:17.130
Because there were repeated invasions

00:55:17.130 --> 00:55:19.950
of the Japanese archipelago from Korea

00:55:19.950 --> 00:55:22.760
over and over again by the Chinese,

00:55:22.760 --> 00:55:24.700
by the mainland Chinese.

